(261,285,'blogs','11','{\"id\":11,\"status\":\"published\",\"sort\":null,\"user_created\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_created\":\"2024-10-11T11:48:39.000Z\",\"user_updated\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_updated\":\"2024-10-14T04:26:30.000Z\",\"content\":\"<h3><strong>Driving in Cambodia: What You Need to Know</strong></h3>\\n<p>If you&rsquo;re planning to rent a car and drive in Cambodia, there are a few things you should know to stay safe and follow the rules of the road. Here&rsquo;s a quick guide to help you navigate the roads in Cambodia.</p>\\n<h4><strong>1. Driving License Requirements</strong></h4>\\n<p>Foreigners need an International Driving Permit (IDP) or a Cambodian driving license to legally drive in Cambodia. Make sure your IDP is up to date before renting a car.</p>\\n<h4><strong>2. Road Conditions</strong></h4>\\n<p>While major roads between cities like Phnom Penh and Siem Reap are paved and in good condition, rural areas often have rough, unpaved roads that can be difficult to navigate, especially during the rainy season. Renting a vehicle with good suspension and clearance is advised for these areas.</p>\\n<h4><strong>3. Traffic Laws</strong></h4>\\n<p>In Cambodia, vehicles drive on the right side of the road. Speed limits are typically 40 km/h in cities and towns and 90 km/h on highways. Be cautious at intersections as traffic can be unpredictable, especially in busy urban areas.</p>\\n<h4><strong>4. Be Prepared for Motorbikes</strong></h4>\\n<p>Motorbikes are common in Cambodia, and they often weave in and out of traffic. Always be on the lookout for motorbikes and give them plenty of space on the road.</p>\\n<p>Understanding these basics will help you stay safe and confident while driving in Cambodia.</p>\",\"thumbnail\":\"c6d2d4e2-a1b6-4f65-abca-bd25abfa3af5\",\"title\":\"Driving in Cambodia: What You Need to Know\",\"description\":\"Essential tips for driving in Cambodia, including road conditions, traffic rules, and driving license requirements, to ensure a safe and smooth journey.\"}','{\"thumbnail\":\"c6d2d4e2-a1b6-4f65-abca-bd25abfa3af5\",\"title\":\"Driving in Cambodia: What You Need to Know\",\"description\":\"Essential tips for driving in Cambodia, including road conditions, traffic rules, and driving license requirements, to ensure a safe and smooth journey.\",\"user_updated\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_updated\":\"2024-10-14T04:26:30.522Z\"}',NULL,NULL),
(262,286,'directus_files','342490ed-c445-43e8-9c00-5c4efe319fa9','{\"folder\":\"afdc5f08-5dcf-4e68-a445-11fca7fa8b7b\",\"title\":\"Designer\",\"filename_download\":\"Designer.jpeg\",\"type\":\"image/jpeg\",\"storage\":\"local\"}','{\"folder\":\"afdc5f08-5dcf-4e68-a445-11fca7fa8b7b\",\"title\":\"Designer\",\"filename_download\":\"Designer.jpeg\",\"type\":\"image/jpeg\",\"storage\":\"local\"}',NULL,NULL),
(263,287,'blogs','12','{\"id\":12,\"status\":\"published\",\"sort\":null,\"user_created\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_created\":\"2024-10-11T11:49:07.000Z\",\"user_updated\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_updated\":\"2024-10-14T04:28:27.000Z\",\"content\":\"<h3><strong>Eco-Friendly Car Rental Options</strong></h3>\\n<p>With environmental concerns on the rise, more travelers are looking for eco-friendly car rental options. Renting a fuel-efficient or hybrid car can help reduce your carbon footprint while exploring new places. Here are some tips for making greener choices when renting a car:</p>\\n<h4><strong>1. Choose a Hybrid or Electric Car</strong></h4>\\n<p>Hybrid and electric cars are becoming more common in car rental fleets. These vehicles use less fuel and produce fewer emissions, making them a great choice for eco-conscious travelers.</p>\\n<h4><strong>2. Opt for a Smaller, Fuel-Efficient Vehicle</strong></h4>\\n<p>If a hybrid isn&rsquo;t available, choosing a smaller, fuel-efficient vehicle like a compact car can still help reduce your fuel consumption and emissions, especially for city driving or short trips.</p>\\n<h4><strong>3. Plan Your Route Efficiently</strong></h4>\\n<p>By planning your route in advance and avoiding unnecessary detours, you can cut down on fuel use and make your trip more eco-friendly. Use GPS or apps to find the shortest routes and avoid traffic congestion.</p>\\n<p>Being mindful of your vehicle choice and driving habits can make a big difference in reducing your environmental impact while traveling.</p>\",\"thumbnail\":\"342490ed-c445-43e8-9c00-5c4efe319fa9\",\"title\":\"Eco-Friendly Car Rental Options\",\"description\":\"Discover how to make environmentally conscious choices when renting a car, including opting for hybrid vehicles and planning fuel-efficient routes.\"}','{\"thumbnail\":\"342490ed-c445-43e8-9c00-5c4efe319fa9\",\"title\":\"Eco-Friendly Car Rental Options\",\"description\":\"Discover how to make environmentally conscious choices when renting a car, including opting for hybrid vehicles and planning fuel-efficient routes.\",\"user_updated\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_updated\":\"2024-10-14T04:28:27.140Z\"}',NULL,NULL),
(264,288,'directus_files','e939617a-1068-4169-86c7-5fa45ff6e665','{\"folder\":\"afdc5f08-5dcf-4e68-a445-11fca7fa8b7b\",\"title\":\"Designer\",\"filename_download\":\"Designer.jpeg\",\"type\":\"image/jpeg\",\"storage\":\"local\"}','{\"folder\":\"afdc5f08-5dcf-4e68-a445-11fca7fa8b7b\",\"title\":\"Designer\",\"filename_download\":\"Designer.jpeg\",\"type\":\"image/jpeg\",\"storage\":\"local\"}',NULL,NULL),
(265,289,'blogs','13','{\"id\":13,\"status\":\"published\",\"sort\":null,\"user_created\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_created\":\"2024-10-11T11:49:20.000Z\",\"user_updated\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_updated\":\"2024-10-14T04:30:05.000Z\",\"content\":\"<h3><strong>The Best Time of Year to Rent a Car in Cambodia</strong></h3>\\n<p>If you&rsquo;re planning a road trip in Cambodia, timing is everything. The country experiences distinct wet and dry seasons, and the time of year can affect road conditions and travel experiences. Here&rsquo;s a breakdown of the best times to rent a car in Cambodia.</p>\\n<h4><strong>1. Dry Season (November to April)</strong></h4>\\n<p>The dry season is the best time for road trips in Cambodia, as roads are generally in better condition and more accessible. This is the perfect time to visit places like Angkor Wat or the beaches of Sihanoukville without worrying about rain.</p>\\n<h4><strong>2. Rainy Season (May to October)</strong></h4>\\n<p>While the rainy season brings lush landscapes and cooler temperatures, it also means muddy and sometimes flooded roads, especially in rural areas. If you plan to travel during the rainy season, consider renting a 4x4 to navigate challenging roads.</p>\\n<h4><strong>3. Festive Periods</strong></h4>\\n<p>The Khmer New Year (mid-April) is a busy time for travel in Cambodia, and renting a car well in advance is recommended as many locals and tourists hit the roads. This is also a great time to experience the country&rsquo;s culture and traditions.</p>\\n<p>By planning your trip around Cambodia&rsquo;s seasons, you can ensure a smoother, more enjoyable journey.</p>\",\"thumbnail\":\"e939617a-1068-4169-86c7-5fa45ff6e665\",\"title\":\"The Best Time of Year to Rent a Car in Cambodia\",\"description\":\"Learn about the ideal times to rent a car in Cambodia, taking into account weather conditions and the impact of wet and dry seasons on road travel.\"}','{\"thumbnail\":\"e939617a-1068-4169-86c7-5fa45ff6e665\",\"title\":\"The Best Time of Year to Rent a Car in Cambodia\",\"description\":\"Learn about the ideal times to rent a car in Cambodia, taking into account weather conditions and the impact of wet and dry seasons on road travel.\",\"user_updated\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_updated\":\"2024-10-14T04:30:05.620Z\"}',NULL,NULL),
(266,290,'directus_files','dab55b6c-b108-4ef7-a9dc-45a9131fec97','{\"folder\":\"afdc5f08-5dcf-4e68-a445-11fca7fa8b7b\",\"title\":\"Designer\",\"filename_download\":\"Designer.jpeg\",\"type\":\"image/jpeg\",\"storage\":\"local\"}','{\"folder\":\"afdc5f08-5dcf-4e68-a445-11fca7fa8b7b\",\"title\":\"Designer\",\"filename_download\":\"Designer.jpeg\",\"type\":\"image/jpeg\",\"storage\":\"local\"}',NULL,NULL),
(267,291,'blogs','14','{\"id\":14,\"status\":\"published\",\"sort\":null,\"user_created\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_created\":\"2024-10-11T11:49:36.000Z\",\"user_updated\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_updated\":\"2024-10-14T04:32:56.000Z\",\"content\":\"<h3><strong>Why You Should Rent a Car for Long-Term Travel</strong></h3>\\n<p>If you&rsquo;re planning an extended stay in Cambodia, renting a car for the long term can offer many benefits over relying on public transportation or taxis. Here&rsquo;s why renting a car is a great option for long-term travel:</p>\\n<h4><strong>1. Cost Savings</strong></h4>\\n<p>Many car rental companies offer discounted rates for long-term rentals, making it more affordable than renting short-term multiple times or using taxis regularly. The cost per day decreases the longer you rent.</p>\\n<h4><strong>2. Convenience and Flexibility</strong></h4>\\n<p>Having your own vehicle gives you the flexibility to explore at your own pace and go wherever you want, whenever you want. There&rsquo;s no need to adhere to bus schedules or pay for multiple taxi rides.</p>\\n<h4><strong>3. Comfort</strong></h4>\\n<p>For long-term travel, comfort becomes essential. Renting a car means you have your own private space to travel in, which is especially beneficial when traveling in rural areas where public transportation can be scarce.</p>\\n<h4><strong>4. Ability to Explore Off-the-Beaten-Path</strong></h4>\\n<p>With your own car, you can explore hidden gems and remote destinations that might be inaccessible via public transportation.</p>\\n<p>Long-term car rentals offer a cost-effective and convenient way to fully experience Cambodia&rsquo;s rich culture and landscapes.</p>\",\"thumbnail\":\"dab55b6c-b108-4ef7-a9dc-45a9131fec97\",\"title\":\"Why You Should Rent a Car for Long-Term Travel\",\"description\":\"Find out why long-term car rentals are a smart option for extended stays, offering convenience, cost savings, and flexibility for people living temporarily in Cambodia.\"}','{\"thumbnail\":\"dab55b6c-b108-4ef7-a9dc-45a9131fec97\",\"title\":\"Why You Should Rent a Car for Long-Term Travel\",\"description\":\"Find out why long-term car rentals are a smart option for extended stays, offering convenience, cost savings, and flexibility for people living temporarily in Cambodia.\",\"user_updated\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_updated\":\"2024-10-14T04:32:56.280Z\"}',NULL,NULL),
