(269,293,'blogs','15','{\"id\":15,\"status\":\"published\",\"sort\":null,\"user_created\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_created\":\"2024-10-11T11:49:56.000Z\",\"user_updated\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_updated\":\"2024-10-14T04:35:42.000Z\",\"content\":\"<h3><strong>Traveling with Pets: What You Need to Know About Car Rentals</strong></h3>\\n<p>If you&rsquo;re traveling with pets, renting a car can make the journey more comfortable for both you and your furry friends. However, there are a few things to keep in mind when renting a car for pet travel:</p>\\n<h4><strong>1. Check the Rental Company&rsquo;s Pet Policy</strong></h4>\\n<p>Before booking, confirm whether the rental company allows pets in their vehicles. Some companies may have restrictions or require an additional cleaning fee.</p>\\n<h4><strong>2. Prepare for Pet Safety</strong></h4>\\n<p>Ensure your pet is safely secured in the vehicle. Consider using a pet seatbelt or crate to keep them safe during the trip. Also, plan for breaks to let your pet stretch and relieve themselves.</p>\\n<h4><strong>3. Bring Pet Essentials</strong></h4>\\n<p>Pack everything your pet will need for the journey, including food, water, leashes, and any necessary medications. It&rsquo;s also a good idea to bring blankets or seat covers to protect the car&rsquo;s upholstery.</p>\\n<p>Renting a car allows for a more pet-friendly travel experience, giving your furry companions a comfortable space for the journey.</p>\",\"thumbnail\":\"abdaa5aa-0f1b-45f5-858e-c9ddebe3dc6f\",\"title\":\"Traveling with Pets: What You Need to Know About Car Rentals\",\"description\":\"A guide for pet-friendly travel in Cambodia, covering rental policies, safety measures for pets, and essential items to bring for a comfortable journey.\"}','{\"thumbnail\":\"abdaa5aa-0f1b-45f5-858e-c9ddebe3dc6f\",\"title\":\"Traveling with Pets: What You Need to Know About Car Rentals\",\"description\":\"A guide for pet-friendly travel in Cambodia, covering rental policies, safety measures for pets, and essential items to bring for a comfortable journey.\",\"user_updated\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_updated\":\"2024-10-14T04:35:42.571Z\"}',NULL,NULL),
