Cambodia without restrictions.</span></p>\",\"user_updated\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_updated\":\"2024-10-14T19:37:50.174Z\"}',NULL,NULL),
(337,363,'blogs','18','{\"id\":18,\"status\":\"published\",\"sort\":null,\"user_created\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_created\":\"2024-10-11T11:51:03.000Z\",\"user_updated\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_updated\":\"2024-10-14T19:37:55.000Z\",\"content\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">Car breakdowns can happen anywhere, but knowing what to do in case of a breakdown in Cambodia can help you stay safe and get back on the road quickly. Here are the steps to take if your rental car breaks down:</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>1. Move to a Safe Area</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">If possible, pull over to the side of the road or move to a safe area. Turn on your hazard lights to alert other drivers.</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>2. Contact the Rental Company</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">Most rental companies provide roadside assistance. Call the rental company&rsquo;s emergency number to report the issue and get help. Be prepared to provide your location and a description of the problem.</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>3. Stay with the Vehicle</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">If you\'re in a remote area, it\'s safer to stay with the vehicle until help arrives. Avoid walking on highways or unfamiliar roads, especially at night.</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>4. Have a Basic Emergency Kit</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">Before heading out, check that your rental car has an emergency kit, including a spare tire, flashlight, and first-aid supplies. This can help you handle minor issues while waiting for assistance.</span></p>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">By staying calm and following these steps, you can manage a car breakdown safely and efficiently.</span></p>\",\"thumbnail\":\"bdf3617a-f6e9-449c-9f3e-0d2158822818\",\"title\":\"What to Do in Case of a Car Breakdown in Cambodia\",\"description\":\"Step-by-step instructions on how to handle a car breakdown in Cambodia, including safety tips, contacting your rental company, and roadside assistance.\",\"tags\":[\"Car Breakdown Tips\",\"Travel Safety\",\"Roadside Assistance\"]}','{\"content\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">Car breakdowns can happen anywhere, but knowing what to do in case of a breakdown in Cambodia can help you stay safe and get back on the road quickly. Here are the steps to take if your rental car breaks down:</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>1. Move to a Safe Area</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">If possible, pull over to the side of the road or move to a safe area. Turn on your hazard lights to alert other drivers.</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>2. Contact the Rental Company</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">Most rental companies provide roadside assistance. Call the rental company&rsquo;s emergency number to report the issue and get help. Be prepared to provide your location and a description of the problem.</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>3. Stay with the Vehicle</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">If you\'re in a remote area, it\'s safer to stay with the vehicle until help arrives. Avoid walking on highways or unfamiliar roads, especially at night.</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>4. Have a Basic Emergency Kit</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">Before heading out, check that your rental car has an emergency kit, including a spare tire, flashlight, and first-aid supplies. This can help you handle minor issues while waiting for assistance.</span></p>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">By staying calm and following these steps, you can manage a car breakdown safely and efficiently.</span></p>\",\"user_updated\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_updated\":\"2024-10-14T19:37:55.429Z\"}',NULL,NULL),
(338,364,'blogs','5','{\"id\":5,\"status\":\"published\",\"sort\":null,\"user_created\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_created\":\"2024-10-11T11:44:25.000Z\",\"user_updated\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_updated\":\"2024-10-14T19:38:47.000Z\",\"content\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">Business travel can be exhausting, especially when dealing with public transportation or taxis. Renting a car for your next business trip can offer several advantages that make your travels more efficient and comfortable:</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>1. Time Management</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">With your own rental car, you won&rsquo;t need to rely on public transit schedules or wait for rideshares. This gives you more control over your time, allowing you to stick to your agenda and avoid delays.</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>2. Professionalism</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">Arriving at meetings in a rental car often makes a more polished impression than using a taxi or rideshare. You can choose a stylish or professional car to fit the tone of your business.</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>3. Flexibility</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">A rental car offers flexibility to adjust your plans on the go. Whether you need to travel between multiple meeting locations or take a last-minute detour to visit a client, you&rsquo;ll have the freedom to move as needed.</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>4. Privacy</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">Rental cars provide a private space to make calls, work on presentations, or relax between meetings. Unlike taxis or public transport, you have the comfort and privacy to prepare for the day ahead.</span></p>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">Renting a car for business trips not only adds convenience but can also elevate the professional aspect of your travels.</span></p>\",\"thumbnail\":\"c3afda90-11fe-4a67-8c60-9ed28c96bfc3\",\"title\":\"Benefits of Renting a Car for Business Travel\",\"description\":\"Discover the advantages of renting a car for business trips, including flexibility, comfort, and how it can enhance productivity and reduce costs compared to other travel options.\",\"tags\":[\"Business Travel Tips\",\"Corporate Car Rentals\",\"Business Travel Solutions\"]}','{\"content\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">Business travel can be exhausting, especially when dealing with public transportation or taxis. Renting a car for your next business trip can offer several advantages that make your travels more efficient and comfortable:</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>1. Time Management</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">With your own rental car, you won&rsquo;t need to rely on public transit schedules or wait for rideshares. This gives you more control over your time, allowing you to stick to your agenda and avoid delays.</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>2. Professionalism</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">Arriving at meetings in a rental car often makes a more polished impression than using a taxi or rideshare. You can choose a stylish or professional car to fit the tone of your business.</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>3. Flexibility</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">A rental car offers flexibility to adjust your plans on the go. Whether you need to travel between multiple meeting locations or take a last-minute detour to visit a client, you&rsquo;ll have the freedom to move as needed.</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>4. Privacy</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">Rental cars provide a private space to make calls, work on presentations, or relax between meetings. Unlike taxis or public transport, you have the comfort and privacy to prepare for the day ahead.</span></p>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">Renting a car for business trips not only adds convenience but can also elevate the professional aspect of your travels.</span></p>\",\"user_updated\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_updated\":\"2024-10-14T19:38:47.407Z\"}',NULL,NULL),
