(694,1008,'blogs','12','{\"id\":12,\"status\":\"published\",\"sort\":null,\"user_created\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_created\":\"2024-10-11T11:49:07.000Z\",\"user_updated\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_updated\":\"2024-11-20T02:18:07.000Z\",\"content\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">With environmental concerns on the rise, more travelers are looking for eco-friendly car rental options. Renting a fuel-efficient or hybrid car can help reduce your carbon footprint while exploring new places. Here are some tips for making greener choices when renting a car:</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>1. Choose a Hybrid or Electric Car</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">Hybrid and electric cars are becoming more common in car rental fleets. These vehicles use less fuel and produce fewer emissions, making them a great choice for eco-conscious travelers.</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>2. Opt for a Smaller, Fuel-Efficient Vehicle</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">If a hybrid isn&rsquo;t available, choosing a smaller, fuel-efficient vehicle like a compact car can still help reduce your fuel consumption and emissions, especially for city driving or short trips.</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>3. Plan Your Route Efficiently</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">By planning your route in advance and avoiding unnecessary detours, you can cut down on fuel use and make your trip more eco-friendly. Use GPS or apps to find the shortest routes and avoid traffic congestion.</span></p>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">Being mindful of your vehicle choice and driving habits can make a big difference in reducing your environmental impact while traveling.</span></p>\",\"title\":\"Eco-Friendly Car Rental Options\",\"description\":\"Discover how to make environmentally conscious choices when renting a car, including opting for hybrid vehicles and planning fuel-efficient routes.\",\"tags\":\"Eco-Friendly Travel, Green Car Rentals, Sustainable Travel\",\"thumbnail\":\"e5073042-03ed-46d4-86b5-6d74e7bdc350\"}','{\"thumbnail\":\"e5073042-03ed-46d4-86b5-6d74e7bdc350\",\"user_updated\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_updated\":\"2024-11-20T02:18:07.207Z\"}',NULL,NULL),
(695,1009,'directus_files','22d90e54-f0c8-4f0c-bfa4-472816b56129','{\"folder\":\"afdc5f08-5dcf-4e68-a445-11fca7fa8b7b\",\"title\":\"Designer (3)\",\"filename_download\":\"Designer (3).jpeg\",\"type\":\"image/jpeg\",\"storage\":\"local\"}','{\"folder\":\"afdc5f08-5dcf-4e68-a445-11fca7fa8b7b\",\"title\":\"Designer (3)\",\"filename_download\":\"Designer (3).jpeg\",\"type\":\"image/jpeg\",\"storage\":\"local\"}',NULL,NULL),
(696,1010,'blogs','13','{\"id\":13,\"status\":\"published\",\"sort\":null,\"user_created\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_created\":\"2024-10-11T11:49:20.000Z\",\"user_updated\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_updated\":\"2024-11-20T02:18:22.000Z\",\"content\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">If you&rsquo;re planning a road trip in Cambodia, timing is everything. The country experiences distinct wet and dry seasons, and the time of year can affect road conditions and travel experiences. Here&rsquo;s a breakdown of the best times to rent a car in Cambodia.</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>1. Dry Season (November to April)</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">The dry season is the best time for road trips in Cambodia, as roads are generally in better condition and more accessible. This is the perfect time to visit places like Angkor Wat or the beaches of Sihanoukville without worrying about rain.</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>2. Rainy Season (May to October)</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">While the rainy season brings lush landscapes and cooler temperatures, it also means muddy and sometimes flooded roads, especially in rural areas. If you plan to travel during the rainy season, consider renting a 4x4 to navigate challenging roads.</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>3. Festive Periods</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">The Khmer New Year (mid-April) is a busy time for travel in Cambodia, and renting a car well in advance is recommended as many locals and tourists hit the roads. This is also a great time to experience the country&rsquo;s culture and traditions.</span></p>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">By planning your trip around Cambodia&rsquo;s seasons, you can ensure a smoother, more enjoyable journey.</span></p>\",\"title\":\"The Best Time of Year to Rent a Car in Cambodia\",\"description\":\"Learn about the ideal times to rent a car in Cambodia, taking into account weather conditions and the impact of wet and dry seasons on road travel.\",\"tags\":\"Car Rental Seasons, Travel Cambodia, Best Travel Time\",\"thumbnail\":\"22d90e54-f0c8-4f0c-bfa4-472816b56129\"}','{\"thumbnail\":\"22d90e54-f0c8-4f0c-bfa4-472816b56129\",\"user_updated\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_updated\":\"2024-11-20T02:18:22.402Z\"}',NULL,NULL),
(697,1011,'directus_files','548159cd-841c-48d6-acbc-6400d7f5451c','{\"folder\":\"afdc5f08-5dcf-4e68-a445-11fca7fa8b7b\",\"title\":\"Designer (4)\",\"filename_download\":\"Designer (4).jpeg\",\"type\":\"image/jpeg\",\"storage\":\"local\"}','{\"folder\":\"afdc5f08-5dcf-4e68-a445-11fca7fa8b7b\",\"title\":\"Designer (4)\",\"filename_download\":\"Designer (4).jpeg\",\"type\":\"image/jpeg\",\"storage\":\"local\"}',NULL,NULL),
(698,1012,'blogs','14','{\"id\":14,\"status\":\"published\",\"sort\":null,\"user_created\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_created\":\"2024-10-11T11:49:36.000Z\",\"user_updated\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_updated\":\"2024-11-20T02:18:40.000Z\",\"content\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">If you&rsquo;re planning an extended stay in Cambodia, renting a car for the long term can offer many benefits over relying on public transportation or taxis. Here&rsquo;s why renting a car is a great option for long-term travel:</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>1. Cost Savings</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">Many car rental companies offer discounted rates for long-term rentals, making it more affordable than renting short-term multiple times or using taxis regularly. The cost per day decreases the longer you rent.</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>2. Convenience and Flexibility</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">Having your own vehicle gives you the flexibility to explore at your own pace and go wherever you want, whenever you want. There&rsquo;s no need to adhere to bus schedules or pay for multiple taxi rides.</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>3. Comfort</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">For long-term travel, comfort becomes essential. Renting a car means you have your own private space to travel in, which is especially beneficial when traveling in rural areas where public transportation can be scarce.</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>4. Ability to Explore Off-the-Beaten-Path</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">With your own car, you can explore hidden gems and remote destinations that might be inaccessible via public transportation.</span></p>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">Long-term car rentals offer a cost-effective and convenient way to fully experience Cambodia&rsquo;s rich culture and landscapes.</span></p>\",\"title\":\"Why You Should Rent a Car for Long-Term Travel\",\"description\":\"Find out why long-term car rentals are a smart option for extended stays, offering convenience, cost savings, and flexibility for people living temporarily in Cambodia.\",\"tags\":\"Long-Term Rentals, Extended Travel, Car Rental Solutions\",\"thumbnail\":\"548159cd-841c-48d6-acbc-6400d7f5451c\"}','{\"thumbnail\":\"548159cd-841c-48d6-acbc-6400d7f5451c\",\"user_updated\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_updated\":\"2024-11-20T02:18:40.436Z\"}',NULL,NULL),
(699,1013,'directus_files','7144ae1f-c553-4468-b9d6-acd649caae68','{\"folder\":\"afdc5f08-5dcf-4e68-a445-11fca7fa8b7b\",\"title\":\"Designer (5)\",\"filename_download\":\"Designer (5).jpeg\",\"type\":\"image/jpeg\",\"storage\":\"local\"}','{\"folder\":\"afdc5f08-5dcf-4e68-a445-11fca7fa8b7b\",\"title\":\"Designer (5)\",\"filename_download\":\"Designer (5).jpeg\",\"type\":\"image/jpeg\",\"storage\":\"local\"}',NULL,NULL),
(700,1014,'blogs','15','{\"id\":15,\"status\":\"published\",\"sort\":null,\"user_created\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_created\":\"2024-10-11T11:49:56.000Z\",\"user_updated\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_updated\":\"2024-11-20T02:19:17.000Z\",\"content\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">If you&rsquo;re traveling with pets, renting a car can make the journey more comfortable for both you and your furry friends. However, there are a few things to keep in mind when renting a car for pet travel:</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>1. Check the Rental Company&rsquo;s Pet Policy</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">Before booking, confirm whether the rental company allows pets in their vehicles. Some companies may have restrictions or require an additional cleaning fee.</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>2. Prepare for Pet Safety</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">Ensure your pet is safely secured in the vehicle. Consider using a pet seatbelt or crate to keep them safe during the trip. Also, plan for breaks to let your pet stretch and relieve themselves.</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>3. Bring Pet Essentials</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">Pack everything your pet will need for the journey, including food, water, leashes, and any necessary medications. It&rsquo;s also a good idea to bring blankets or seat covers to protect the car&rsquo;s upholstery.</span></p>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">Renting a car allows for a more pet-friendly travel experience, giving your furry companions a comfortable space for the journey.</span></p>\",\"title\":\"Traveling with Pets: What You Need to Know About Car Rentals\",\"description\":\"A guide for pet-friendly travel in Cambodia, covering rental policies, safety measures for pets, and essential items to bring for a comfortable journey.\",\"tags\":\"Pet-Friendly Travel, Traveling with Pets, Car Rentals for Pets\",\"thumbnail\":\"7144ae1f-c553-4468-b9d6-acd649caae68\"}','{\"thumbnail\":\"7144ae1f-c553-4468-b9d6-acd649caae68\",\"user_updated\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_updated\":\"2024-11-20T02:19:17.776Z\"}',NULL,NULL),
