(702,1016,'blogs','16','{\"id\":16,\"status\":\"published\",\"sort\":null,\"user_created\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_created\":\"2024-10-11T11:50:34.000Z\",\"user_updated\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_updated\":\"2024-11-20T02:19:29.000Z\",\"content\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">From weddings to anniversaries, special occasions often call for something extraordinary. Renting a luxury car can add a touch of elegance to your big event. Here are some of the best options for different occasions:</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>1. Weddings</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">For weddings, renting a luxury sedan or a vintage car can make your special day even more memorable. Many rental companies offer chauffeur services for added convenience and style.</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>2. Anniversaries</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">Celebrate your anniversary with a luxury or convertible car, perfect for a romantic getaway. These cars provide both comfort and style, making the trip as memorable as the occasion itself.</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>3. Corporate Events</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">For corporate events, renting an executive car like a BMW or Mercedes can elevate your professional image. These cars offer comfort and luxury, ensuring you arrive at your event in style.</span></p>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">For any special occasion, renting a luxury vehicle can enhance the experience and make your celebration even more unforgettable.</span></p>\",\"title\":\"Renting a Car for Special Occasions in Cambodia\",\"description\":\"Highlight how renting a luxury or special vehicle can enhance celebrations like weddings, anniversaries, and corporate events, adding elegance and style.\",\"tags\":\"Special Occasion Rentals, Event Car Rentals, Luxury Car Rentals\",\"thumbnail\":\"3a7484eb-5863-4d4a-a361-49e308940ca3\"}','{\"thumbnail\":\"3a7484eb-5863-4d4a-a361-49e308940ca3\",\"user_updated\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_updated\":\"2024-11-20T02:19:29.809Z\"}',NULL,NULL),
(703,1017,'directus_files','83e3450f-311c-4100-9c12-2daa14820d41','{\"folder\":\"afdc5f08-5dcf-4e68-a445-11fca7fa8b7b\",\"title\":\"Designer (7)\",\"filename_download\":\"Designer (7).jpeg\",\"type\":\"image/jpeg\",\"storage\":\"local\"}','{\"folder\":\"afdc5f08-5dcf-4e68-a445-11fca7fa8b7b\",\"title\":\"Designer (7)\",\"filename_download\":\"Designer (7).jpeg\",\"type\":\"image/jpeg\",\"storage\":\"local\"}',NULL,NULL),
(704,1018,'blogs','17','{\"id\":17,\"status\":\"published\",\"sort\":null,\"user_created\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_created\":\"2024-10-11T11:50:48.000Z\",\"user_updated\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_updated\":\"2024-11-20T02:22:12.000Z\",\"content\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">When planning a long road trip in Cambodia, opting for a rental car with unlimited mileage can be a smart decision. Here&rsquo;s why unlimited mileage rentals are beneficial:</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>1. Freedom to Explore</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">With unlimited mileage, you can travel as far as you want without worrying about extra charges. This is perfect for road trips where you want the flexibility to explore multiple destinations.</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>2. Cost Efficiency</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">If you plan on covering a lot of ground, unlimited mileage can save you money in the long run, as you won&rsquo;t have to pay per mile. This is especially useful for longer trips across Cambodia.</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>3. Less Stress</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">Unlimited mileage rentals allow you to focus on your trip rather than keeping track of how many miles you&rsquo;ve driven. This can make your travel experience more enjoyable and relaxing.</span></p>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">Renting a car with unlimited mileage offers peace of mind and the freedom to fully explore Cambodia without restrictions.</span></p>\",\"title\":\"The Advantages of Renting a Car with Unlimited Mileage\",\"description\":\"Learn the benefits of renting a car with unlimited mileage, offering freedom, cost efficiency, and flexibility for long road trips across Cambodia.\",\"tags\":\"Unlimited Mileage, Car Rental Benefits\",\"thumbnail\":\"83e3450f-311c-4100-9c12-2daa14820d41\"}','{\"thumbnail\":\"83e3450f-311c-4100-9c12-2daa14820d41\",\"user_updated\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_updated\":\"2024-11-20T02:22:12.615Z\"}',NULL,NULL),
(705,1019,'directus_files','ff7b04f8-4d9c-4121-bf83-53304f131987','{\"folder\":\"afdc5f08-5dcf-4e68-a445-11fca7fa8b7b\",\"title\":\"Designer (8)\",\"filename_download\":\"Designer (8).jpeg\",\"type\":\"image/jpeg\",\"storage\":\"local\"}','{\"folder\":\"afdc5f08-5dcf-4e68-a445-11fca7fa8b7b\",\"title\":\"Designer (8)\",\"filename_download\":\"Designer (8).jpeg\",\"type\":\"image/jpeg\",\"storage\":\"local\"}',NULL,NULL),
(706,1020,'blogs','18','{\"id\":18,\"status\":\"published\",\"sort\":null,\"user_created\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_created\":\"2024-10-11T11:51:03.000Z\",\"user_updated\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_updated\":\"2024-11-20T02:22:24.000Z\",\"content\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">Car breakdowns can happen anywhere, but knowing what to do in case of a breakdown in Cambodia can help you stay safe and get back on the road quickly. Here are the steps to take if your rental car breaks down:</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>1. Move to a Safe Area</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">If possible, pull over to the side of the road or move to a safe area. Turn on your hazard lights to alert other drivers.</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>2. Contact the Rental Company</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">Most rental companies provide roadside assistance. Call the rental company&rsquo;s emergency number to report the issue and get help. Be prepared to provide your location and a description of the problem.</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>3. Stay with the Vehicle</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">If you\'re in a remote area, it\'s safer to stay with the vehicle until help arrives. Avoid walking on highways or unfamiliar roads, especially at night.</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>4. Have a Basic Emergency Kit</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">Before heading out, check that your rental car has an emergency kit, including a spare tire, flashlight, and first-aid supplies. This can help you handle minor issues while waiting for assistance.</span></p>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">By staying calm and following these steps, you can manage a car breakdown safely and efficiently.</span></p>\",\"title\":\"What to Do in Case of a Car Breakdown in Cambodia\",\"description\":\"Step-by-step instructions on how to handle a car breakdown in Cambodia, including safety tips, contacting your rental company, and roadside assistance.\",\"tags\":\"Car Breakdown Tips, Travel Safety, Roadside Assistance\",\"thumbnail\":\"ff7b04f8-4d9c-4121-bf83-53304f131987\"}','{\"thumbnail\":\"ff7b04f8-4d9c-4121-bf83-53304f131987\",\"user_updated\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_updated\":\"2024-11-20T02:22:24.821Z\"}',NULL,NULL),
(707,1044,'blogs','11','{\"id\":11,\"status\":\"published\",\"sort\":null,\"user_created\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_created\":\"2024-10-11T11:48:39.000Z\",\"user_updated\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_updated\":\"2024-11-20T02:24:25.000Z\",\"content\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">If you&rsquo;re planning to rent a car and drive in Cambodia, there are a few things you should know to stay safe and follow the rules of the road. Here&rsquo;s a quick guide to help you navigate the roads in Cambodia.</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>1. Driving License Requirements</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">Foreigners need an International Driving Permit (IDP) or a Cambodian driving license to legally drive in Cambodia. Make sure your IDP is up to date before renting a car.</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>2. Road Conditions</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">While major roads between cities like Phnom Penh and Siem Reap are paved and in good condition, rural areas often have rough, unpaved roads that can be difficult to navigate, especially during the rainy season. Renting a vehicle with good suspension and clearance is advised for these areas.</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>3. Traffic Laws</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">In Cambodia, vehicles drive on the right side of the road. Speed limits are typically 40 km/h in cities and towns and 90 km/h on highways. Be cautious at intersections as traffic can be unpredictable, especially in busy urban areas.</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>4. Be Prepared for Motorbikes</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">Motorbikes are common in Cambodia, and they often weave in and out of traffic. Always be on the lookout for motorbikes and give them plenty of space on the road.</span></p>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">Understanding these basics will help you stay safe and confident while driving in Cambodia.</span></p>\",\"title\":\"Driving in Cambodia: What You Need to Know\",\"description\":\"Essential tips for driving in Cambodia, including road conditions, traffic rules, and driving license requirements, to ensure a safe and smooth journey.\",\"tags\":\"Driving in Cambodia, Travel Cambodia, Road Safety\",\"thumbnail\":\"65a50677-ef7d-4092-b7ea-493372dc151c\"}','{\"thumbnail\":\"65a50677-ef7d-4092-b7ea-493372dc151c\",\"user_updated\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_updated\":\"2024-11-20T02:24:25.856Z\"}',NULL,NULL),
(708,1045,'blogs','12','{\"id\":12,\"status\":\"published\",\"sort\":null,\"user_created\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_created\":\"2024-10-11T11:49:07.000Z\",\"user_updated\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_updated\":\"2024-11-20T02:24:38.000Z\",\"content\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">With environmental concerns on the rise, more travelers are looking for eco-friendly car rental options. Renting a fuel-efficient or hybrid car can help reduce your carbon footprint while exploring new places. Here are some tips for making greener choices when renting a car:</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>1. Choose a Hybrid or Electric Car</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">Hybrid and electric cars are becoming more common in car rental fleets. These vehicles use less fuel and produce fewer emissions, making them a great choice for eco-conscious travelers.</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>2. Opt for a Smaller, Fuel-Efficient Vehicle</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">If a hybrid isn&rsquo;t available, choosing a smaller, fuel-efficient vehicle like a compact car can still help reduce your fuel consumption and emissions, especially for city driving or short trips.</span></p>\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\"><strong>3. Plan Your Route Efficiently</strong></span></h4>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">By planning your route in advance and avoiding unnecessary detours, you can cut down on fuel use and make your trip more eco-friendly. Use GPS or apps to find the shortest routes and avoid traffic congestion.</span></p>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">Being mindful of your vehicle choice and driving habits can make a big difference in reducing your environmental impact while traveling.</span></p>\",\"title\":\"Eco-Friendly Car Rental Options\",\"description\":\"Discover how to make environmentally conscious choices when renting a car, including opting for hybrid vehicles and planning fuel-efficient routes.\",\"tags\":\"Eco-Friendly Travel, Green Car Rentals, Sustainable Travel\",\"thumbnail\":\"c5a52367-2271-4bcd-93b4-82da65e341af\"}','{\"thumbnail\":\"c5a52367-2271-4bcd-93b4-82da65e341af\",\"user_updated\":\"8bf1a523-5059-4ece-8f55-cc361500b3d0\",\"date_updated\":\"2024-11-20T02:24:38.361Z\"}',NULL,NULL),
